<p>Greetings Zamarak500, and welcome to the new year of the site. Being a history buff is both awesome(fellow history buff) and helpful since historical knowledge can always help bolster a good article. Also Roman history is just neat. And well maybe you have been here before, but we made you forget? Who knows? Make sure to take your time and get acquainted with how everything here works, and make sure to check out <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/chat-guide">IRC</a> chat too!</p>
<p>For my recommendation, you should check out <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5700">SCP-5700</a></p>
